title: Ну-ка все вместе: Битва сезонов.
overview: In each qualifying round of the special project, the strongest participants will compete for the title of super winner, who in the future will open the grandiose fifth, anniversary season of the show. As always, in the position of the leading People's Artist of Russia, the unsurpassed Nikolai Baskov. By tradition, guest stars will also take the stage in a special project.
